---
pageable: true
per_page: 10
---


<div id="container">
  <aside class="side-nav">
    <div id="avatar">
    </div>
    <h1>Hi, I'm Evan</h1>
    <p>I am a graduate of <a class="link" style="font-weight:bold" target="_blank" href="https://www.insead.edu/">INSEAD</a> (MBA class of 21D)
      and the co-founder of <a class="link" style="font-weight:bold" target="_blank" href="https://well-sprout.com/">Wellsprout</a>, 
      a 100% natural plant-based supergreens powder formulated to help time-strapped professionals to care for their gut health and energy.
    <p>I previously built a social network for collecting and sharing new ideas, worked as a Technical Program Manager at <a class="link" style="font-weight:bold" target="_blank" href="https://www.grab.com/">Grab</a> (a super-app unicorn in Southeast Asia), 
      and was also Chief of Staff at a data analytics software-as-a service startup.
    <p>Having worked with many companies and startups making a difference through building great products and deploying game-changing solutions, 
      I believe in following my energy, and enjoy finding ways to use technology, software and data to take action and operationalise visions into reality, 
      to do meaningful work and build purposeful careers.
    <p>I coded this site on Ruby using Middleman Blog and GitHub Pages.
    </p>
  </aside>

  <div id="social-container">
    <div id="social-li">
      <button class="btn" onclick="window.open('https://www.linkedin.com/in/evantanbk/','_blank')">
        <img class="social" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/evtan/evtan.github.io/source/data/linkedin.png">
      </button>
    </div>
    <div id="social-twitter">
      <button class="btn" onclick="window.open('https://twitter.com/evtan','_blank')">
        <img class="social" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/evtan/evtan.github.io/source/data/twitter.png">
      </button>
    </div>
    <div id="social-gh">
      <button class="btn" onclick="window.open('https://github.com/evtan','_blank')">
        <img class="social" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/evtan/evtan.github.io/source/data/github.png">
      </button>
    </div>
    <div id="social-medium">
      <button class="btn" onclick="window.open('https://medium.com/@evtan','_blank')">
        <img class="social" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/evtan/evtan.github.io/source/data/medium.png">
      </button>
    </div>
    <div id="social-wellsprout">
      <button class="btn" onclick="window.open('https://well-sprout.com','_blank')">
        <img class="social" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/evtan/evtan.github.io/source/data/wellsprout.png">
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="container">
  <h3>Recent Articles</h3>
    <% blog.articles[0...10].each do |article, i| %>
      <li><b><%= link_to article.title, article, :class => 'link' %></b> <span><%= article.date.strftime('%e %b %Y') %></span></li>
    <% end %>
</div>

<% if paginate && num_pages > 1 %>
  <p>Page <%= page_number %> of <%= num_pages %></p>

  <% if prev_page %>
    <p><%= link_to 'Previous page', prev_page %></p>
  <% end %>
<% end %>

<% if paginate %>
  <% if next_page %>
    <p><%= link_to 'Next page', next_page %></p>
  <% end %>
<% end %>
